"panda\">\n{{cite web\n |date        = 27 June 2014\n |title       = Snow leopard, red panda get new conservation centre in Darjeeling\n |work        = [[The Indian Express]]\n |url         = http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/kolkata/snow-leopard-red-panda-get-new-conservation-centre-in-darjeeling/\n |accessdate  = 21 November 2015\n |url-status=live\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20151122111421/http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/kolkata/snow-leopard-red-panda-get-new-conservation-centre-in-darjeeling/\n |archivedate = 22 November 2015\n |df          = dmy-all\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<!--ref name=\"ExpressIndia2008-03-11\">{{cite web| author = Express news service| date = 11 March 2008| title = Ghisingh gone, Morcha \u2018closer\u2019 to Gorkhaland| work = Express India| publisher = [[The Indian Express]]| url = http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/Ghisingh-gone-Morcha-closer-to-Gorkhaland/282846/| accessdate = 15 June 2011}}</ref-->\n\n<ref name=\"Dam2009-06-11\">\n{{cite web\n |last=Dam\n |first=Mohana\n |date=11 June 2009\n |title=Darjeeling to ban plastic altogether\n |work=Express India\n |publisher=[[The Indian Express]]\n |url=http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/darjeeling-to-ban-plastic-altogether/474728/\n |accessdate=15 June 2011\n |url-status=dead\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314231251/http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/darjeeling-to-ban-plastic-altogether/474728/\n |archivedate=14 March 2012\n \n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Haber2004-01-14\">\n{{cite news\n |last=Haber\n |first=Daniel B.\n |date=14 January 2004\n |title=Economy-India: Famed Darjeeling Tea Growers Eye Tourism for Survival\n |publisher=Inter Press Service News Agency\n |url=http://www.ipsnews.net/africa/interna.asp?idnews=21909\n |accessdate=8 May 2006\n |url-status=dead\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060602163603/http://www.ipsnews.net/africa/interna.asp?idnews=21909\n |archivedate=2 June 2006\n \n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BBC2001-07-27\">\n{{cite news\n |title       = Darjeeling tea growers at risk\n |date        = 27 July 2001\n |work   = BBC News\n |url         = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/1456988.stm\n |accessdate  = 15 June 2011\n |url-status=live\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20120327184751/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/1456988.stm\n |archivedate = 27 March 2012\n |df          = dmy-all\n}}\n</ref>\n\n}}\n\n== References ==\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Aftab | first = Aaris\n  | year = 2005\n  | title = Are the Third World cities sustainable?\n  | publisher = Allied Publishers\n  | page = 201\n  | isbn = 978-81-7764-869-0\n  | url = https://books.google.com/?id=R1HV6aoINaQC\n  | accessdate =\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite journal\n  | last = Dasgupta | first = Atis\n  | year = 1999\n  | title = Ethnic Problems and Movements for Autonomy in Darjeeling\n  | periodical = Social Scientist\n  | volume = 27\n  | issue = 11\u201312\n  | pages = 47\u201368\n  | doi = 10.2307/3518047\n  | jstor = 3518047\n  | ref = harv\n  | publisher = Social Scientist\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last1 = de Bruyn | first1 = Pippa|last2=Bain|first2=Keith|last3=Venkatraman|first3=Nilofer|last4=Joshi|first4=Shonar\n  | year = 2008\n  | title = Frommer's India\n  | publisher = Frommer's\n  | isbn = 978-0-470-16908-7\n  | url = https://books.google.com/?id=qMqBvtL_nI0C&pg=PA578&dq=how+to+get+to+darjeeling#v=onepage&q=how%20to%20get%20to%20darjeeling&f=false\n  | accessdate = 8 January 2011\n  | ref = harv\n  }}\n* {{cite book\n  | last = Gerard\n  | first = John\n  | year = 1990\n  | title = Mountain environments: an examination of the physical geography of mountains\n  | page = [https://archive.org/details/mountainenvironm0000gerr/page/317 317]\n  | publisher = MIT Press\n  | isbn = 978-0-262-07128-4\n  | ref = harv\n  | url = https://archive.org/details/mountainenvironm0000gerr/page/317\n  }}\n* {{cite journal\n  | doi = 10.1111/j.1467-8306.1995.tb01821.x\n  | last = Kenny | 