rd, red panda get new conservation centre in Darjeeling\n |work        = [[The Indian Express]]\n |url         = http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/kolkata/snow-leopard-red-panda-get-new-conservation-centre-in-darjeeling/\n |accessdate  = 21 November 2015\n |url-status=live\n |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20151122111421/http://indianexpress.com/article/cities/kolkata/snow-leopard-red-panda-get-new-conservation-centre-in-darjeeling/\n |archivedate = 22 November 2015\n |df          = dmy-all\n}}\n</ref>\n\n<!--ref name=\"ExpressIndia2008-03-11\">{{cite web| author = Express news service| date = 11 March 2008| title = Ghisingh gone, Morcha \u2018closer\u2019 to Gorkhaland| work = Express India| publisher = [[The Indian Express]]| url = http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/Ghisingh-gone-Morcha-closer-to-Gorkhaland/282846/| accessdate = 15 June 2011}}</ref-->\n\n<ref name=\"Dam2009-06-11\">\n{{cite web\n |last=Dam\n |first=Mohana\n |date=11 June 2009\n |title=Darjeeling to ban plastic altogether\n |work=Express India\n |publisher=[[The Indian Express]]\n |url=http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/darjeeling-to-ban-plastic-altogether/474728/\n |accessdate=15 June 2011\n |url-status=dead\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314231251/http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/darjeeling-to-ban-plastic-altogether/474728/\n |archivedate=14 March 2012\n \n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Haber2004-01-14\">\n{{cite news\n |last=Haber\n |first=Daniel B.\n |date=14 January 2004\n |title=Economy-India: Famed Darjeeling Tea Growers Eye Tourism for Survival\n |publisher=Inter Press Service News Agency\n |url=http://www.ipsnews.net/africa/interna.asp?idnews=21909\n |accessdate=8 May 2006\n |url-status=dead\n |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060602163603/http://www.ipsnews.net/africa/interna.asp?idnews=21909\n |archivedate=2 June 2006\n \n}}\n</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"BBC2001-07-27\">\n{{cite news\n |title       = Darjeeling tea growers at risk\n |date    